data.title: Tech. Sgt. Honea
data.meta_description: Talks to a military reporter about the tasks of his combat communications unit, their current mission, the importance of their communications equipment to the military operations in the area, what he enjoys about his work and the importance of safety to their small crew. Also see "Staff Sgt. McCullough" in this section and "Bright Star Antenna Set Up" in the B-roll section.
